0:00:06.962344463 25154 0x7f665405cf20 INFO               GST_EVENT gstevent.c:814:gst_event_new_caps: creating caps event audio/x-raw, format=(string)F32LE, layout=(string)interleaved, rate=(int)44100, channels=(int)2, channel-mask=(bitmask)0x0000000000000003
0:00:06.962364820 25154 0x7f665405cf20 INFO                GST_PADS gstpad.c:4232:gst_pad_peer_query:<audioconvert0:src> pad has no peer
